This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with machine translation, which is a subfield of natural language processing. It is also likely to belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it discusses the use of neural machine translation systems. Additionally, it could belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as machine translation is a subfield of AI. It may also belong to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it discusses the use of neural networks in machine translation. Finally, it could belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) as some of the techniques used in machine translation, such as attention mechanisms, are also used in computer vision.
